               <p>MARY BROWN. I am the wife of John Brown, and live in <placeName id="t18311020-83-crimeloc444">Pelham-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18311020-83-crimeloc444" type="placeName" value="Pelham-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18311020-83-crimeloc444" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311020-83-off442 t18311020-83-crimeloc444"></join>. The prisoner worked in my shop for five or six weeks, and slept there - on the morning of the 6th of October I missed twenty shuttles out of a loom, which was standing in the shop - I then went to another loom, and missed twenty more.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18311020-83-person658">
                  WILLIAM 
