            . I am servant to Mr. Sowerby, a pawnbroker. I have twenty shuttles, pawned with me by the prisoner, on the 1st of October, for 1s.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18311020-83-person659">
                  DICKENSON 
                  SOWERBY
