            . I am master of the shop. I have twenty shuttles pawned with me, by some boy, on the 28th of September.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18311020-83-person660">
                  HENRY 
                  BOLTON
